## Troubleshooting

### "Connection refused"
- Service not running
- Wrong port
- Run: `e2e observe` to detect correct port

### "No services configured"
- Edit `e2e.conf` to add your service
- Or run: `e2e set url my-api http://localhost:8080`

### Tests fail
- Check service is running: `curl http://localhost:8080/health`
- Verify URL in `e2e.conf`
- Run with debug: `e2e run --debug`
